OL,6,FGranada Reports journalist Ann
OL,7,FO'Connor went to the drama workshop
OL,8,Fthat aims to stop children being
OL,9,Fgroomed into joining drugs gangs.
OL,11,FChildren are being given lessons that
OL,12,Fcould save them from being groomed by
OL,13,Fdrugs gangs.
OL,15,FThe 'Grassing or Grooming' resource is
OL,16,Fdesigned to help children identify and
OL,17,Fresist grooming linked to gangs and
OL,18,Fviolent crime.
