OL,3,CPrimary school pupils warned about
OL,4,Cdrug gang grooming in drama workshops
OL,6,FSupported by Merseyside Police, it
OL,7,Ffocuses on helping young people to
OL,8,Frecognise the warning signs of abuse
OL,9,Fand report it when they have concerns.
OL,11,FThe pupils take part in a drama
OL,12,Fworkshop. It shows what could happen
OL,13,Fto their friends who are at first
OL,14,Fbombarded with expensive presents,
OL,15,Fthen drawn into ferrying mystery
OL,16,Fpackages around their area.
OL,18,FBecoming a puppet on powerful string
OL,19,Fis how the boys and girls at Rock
OL,20,FFerry Primary see grooming.
