OL,3,CPrimary school pupils warned about
OL,4,Cdrug gang grooming in drama workshops
OL,6,FThe programme by the educational
OL,7,Fcharity Ariel Trust is aimed at
OL,8,Fprimary age pupils and is part of the
OL,9,Farea's plans to reduce violence.
OL,11,FDuring these sessions, pupils are
OL,12,Fencouraged to step into the role of
OL,13,Fbystander, victim and perpetrator,
OL,14,Fhelping them to learn the skills to
OL,15,Fintervene or ask for help.
OL,17,FThe programme has been delivered in
OL,18,Fmore than 100 schools across
OL,19,FMerseyside since it was first launched
OL,20,Fin 2021.
