OL,6,FIt was independently evaluated by
OL,7,FLiverpool John Moore's University
OL,8,Fresearchers last year who found after
OL,9,Ftaking part in the training, pupils
OL,10,Ffelt 55% more confident explaining
OL,11,Fwhat grooming means to a friend.
OL,13,FMerseyside Police Commissioner Emily
OL,14,FSpurrell supports the programme.
OL,16,FRock Ferry Primary School Headteacher
OL,17,FSara Radley said: "The Ariel Trust's
OL,18,FGrassing and Grooming Project has had
OL,19,Fa profound impact on pupils at Rock
OL,20,FFerry, significantly increasing their
OL,21,Fawareness of online grooming risks.
