OL,6,FDirector of the Merseyside Violence
OL,7,FReduction Partnership Supt Georgie
OL,8,FGarvey said: "We're passionate about
OL,9,Fempowering young people with the
OL,10,Fknowledge and the tools to protect
OL,11,Fthemselves, both in the real and the
OL,12,Fonline world.
OL,14,F"This is a pivotal age for children,
OL,15,Fas they prepare for secondary school
OL,16,Fand exposure to a more grown-up world
OL,17,F- a world in which social media will
OL,18,Fbe no doubt be a big part of their
OL,19,Flives.
